                    <p>天猫【咏鹅庄旗舰店】</p><p>咏鹅庄 · 霞多丽 · 干白葡萄酒 750ml 日常售价 98 元，下单立减 20 元，领取 40 元优惠券。</p><p><span class="font-color-red"><strong>点击详情页【享大额补贴】卡片</strong></span>，淘金币可抵扣 5.94 元，到手价 32.06 元：</p><dir><a contenteditable="false" href="https://uland.taobao.com/coupon/edetail?e=1F49FBzeGwGlhHvvyUNXZfh8CuWt5YH5OVuOuRD5gLJMmdsrkidbOWBzzpT26idJOK4cLKuQKL9DT6kkPP4sVURzTJIXnXwvNTxBe%2FT7sfTOMZevD3nnTPpItCfznyHe2mwCY5fS7rVrTdT7cgXf6jgYSYpxmYtMsb%2Bvi71p7YhlXymvoVZzQy7Sr3jPkQAmCXOwM%2F44tlASwGdedzkKTBHtR5M9fhgNtsfGA5CFJLDe4LCSMIu01NeqSq5uaIh97jKjAO7pxYgdIMeVz1KiUX4%2BWynxxEEN2beGRAGSLEXY2EfcqMd5KPRaof9OaBAvKy%2FEbpUvVz%2BuTmgRnC%2FRkkwNBUbTsArs&amp;traceId=2150464517831717112306075e0c88&amp;&amp;union_lens=lensId:TAPI@1783171711@213dc86f_1484_19f2d51013f_bfa2@01" target="_blank"><span class="card main-site"><span class="card-logo"><img height="820" src="https://img.alicdn.com/bao/uploaded/i4/2222291903867/O1CN01L3Lapt1eR8ioVOcEC_!!4611686018427381115-0-item_pic.jpg" title="宁夏贺兰山麓酿造：咏鹅庄霞多丽干白葡萄酒 98 → 32 元官方破冰新低" width="1200" /></span><span class="card-info"><span class="card-title"><span class="mall-data">天猫</span><span class="card-name">咏鹅庄 白葡萄酒</span></span><span class="card-abstract">霞多丽 干型</span><span class="card-controls"><span class="price">淘金币抵扣后 32.06 元</span><span class="card-btn-deep">领 40 元券</span></span></span></span></a></dir><p>京东旗舰店日常售价 78 元：<a href="https://u.jd.com/XaADLnm" target="_blank">点此查看</a>。</p><ul class=" list-paddingleft-2"><li><p style="text-align: left;">葡萄产地：宁夏臻麓酒庄</p></li><li><p style="text-align: left;">葡萄品种：霞多丽</p></li><li><p style="text-align: left;">酒精度：11.8% vol</p></li><li><p style="text-align: left;">葡萄酒原料：鲜葡萄、食品添加剂（焦亚硫酸钾）</p></li><li><p style="text-align: left;">类型：半型（Dry）</p></li></ul><p style="text-align: left;">酒体呈浅禾秆黄色，散发着柠檬、柑橘和成熟白桃、香瓜等水果芳香，入口酸度适宜，不失清爽口感，余味爽净悠长。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="1054" src="https://img.alicdn.com/imgextra/i1/2222291903867/O1CN01yyWQA41eR8iqA7ZCc_!!2222291903867.jpg" title="宁夏贺兰山麓酿造：咏鹅庄霞